title: DAZ3D - Tourist Poses for Genesis 3
description:
As every good tourist knows, your travels are as good as your map. Give your Genesis 3 characters the chance to see the world with these thoughtfully crafted tourist poses and realistic 3D map model. Poses include both male and female versions in both single stance and two-person vignette poses. The map model comes with 21 morphs to create the realistic movement of an actual map.

As always, FeralFey poses are fact checked for gravity, weight, and realism.
